data.description: 3 Bedrooms, 2 full bathroom, Rancher, Located in West York School District. This home features: Living room with hardwood flooring, ceiling fan and bay window. Den with laminate flooring, and built in cabinets. Dining area with hardwood flooring and ceiling fan. Open Eat-In Kitchen with bay window, island, refrigerator, Electric range and double oven, dishwasher, recessed lights, ceiling fans and sliding glass door giving access to deck. Full bathroom features tile flooring, single vanity, soaking tub and tile surround, and stall shower.  3 Bedrooms with hardwood flooring, closet and ceiling fan. In the basement, you will find a family room with laminate flooring, ceiling fan, gas fireplace and walk out stairs to backyard brick patio. Rec room with laminate flooring and ceiling fan. Laundry hook up and two additional rooms for storage. Moving outside, Deck overlooking backyard, brick patio and chain link fencing.
